text: Key Exchange is a 1985 American romantic comedy movie directed by Barnet Kellman and based on the play of the same name by Kevin Wade. It stars Brooke Adams, Danny Aiello, Ben Masters, Kerry Armstrong, Annie Golden and was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1985 romantic comedy movies Category:American romantic comedy movies Category:Movies based on plays Category:20th Century Fox movies
